      <title>6万亿欧元投资者警告欧盟不要放松绿色规则</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/investors-with-6-trillion-euros-warn-eu-not-weaken-green-rules-2025-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁塞尔正在制定计划，减少绿色金融方面的繁琐手续，管理着 6.6 万亿欧元资产的投资者敦促欧盟不要放松其可持续发展规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/investors-with-6-trillion-euros-warn-eu-not-weaken-green-rules-2025-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
